00:22:44.480 --> 00:22:47.630 align:middle line:84%
How is what you do
different than meditation?

00:22:47.630 --> 00:22:49.620 align:middle line:84%
>>FRENETTE:
Meditation-- you mean

00:22:49.620 --> 00:22:51.060 align:middle line:90%
