centering prayer

00:22:57.260 --> 00:23:00.220 align:middle line:84%
and those great
meditative traditions

00:23:00.220 --> 00:23:03.620 align:middle line:84%
emphasize practice and
emphasize coming out

00:23:03.620 --> 00:23:07.860 align:middle line:84%
of a living tradition of
practitioners for many years,

00:23:07.860 --> 00:23:11.280 align:middle line:84%
and opening up to a mystery
that's not necessarily

00:23:11.280 --> 00:23:15.150 align:middle line:84%
about dogma and belief
alone, but about experience

00:23:15.150 --> 00:23:20.020 align:middle line:84%
and the transformation of the
structures of consciousness.

00:23:20.020 --> 00:23:22.360 align:middle line:84%
I'm trained in
psychology, so that's

00:23:22.360 --> 00:23:27.280 align:middle line:84%
like a unifying language now
between all the religions.

00:23:27.280 --> 00:23:32.190 align:middle line:84%
So there are similarities, and
there's a sense of difference,

00:23:32.190 --> 00:23:35.810 align:middle line:84%
too, and uniqueness, I think,
to all the great traditions.

00:23:35.810 --> 00:23:39.450 align:middle line:84%
I guess if you
climb a mountain--

00:23:39.450 --> 00:23:41.610 align:middle line:84%
and your question
is are those paths

00:23:41.610 --> 00:23:43.340 align:middle line:90%
leading to the same place?

00:23:43.340 --> 00:23:45.660 align:middle line:84%
So is the meditative
path of Buddhism

00:23:45.660 --> 00:23:48.040 align:middle line:84%
leading to the same
place on the mountain?

00:23:48.040 --> 00:23:52.510 align:middle line:84%
Is the Christian contemplative
path leading to the same place?

00:23:52.510 --> 00:23:56.940 align:middle line:84%
Well, within that metaphor,
I think, probably, they

00:23:56.940 --> 00:23:58.800 align:middle line:90%
are leading to the same place.

00:23:58.800 --> 00:24:02.225 align:middle line:84%
But maybe they're different
routes up the mountain--

00:24:02.225 --> 00:24:03.100 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: To get there.

00:24:03.100 --> 00:24:06.154 align:middle line:84%
>>FRENETTE: To get there-- open
up a slightly different view,

00:24:06.154 --> 00:24:08.320 align:middle line:84%
and they're slightly different
paths and everything,

00:24:08.320 --> 00:24:11.380 align:middle line:84%
but I trust that the
summit, or the depths,

00:24:11.380 --> 00:24:13.000 align:middle line:84%
if you don't want
to use that kind

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:17.170 align:middle line:84%
of heightened, hierarchical
imagery, is the same.

00:24:17.170 --> 00:24:19.820 align:middle line:84%
So in centering prayer,
one of the differences

00:24:19.820 --> 00:24:27.710 align:middle line:84%
that's probably unique, if not
exclusive, to centering prayer

00:24:27.710 --> 00:24:30.160 align:middle line:90%
is this idea of relationship.

00:24:30.160 --> 00:24:36.390 align:middle line:84%
So that practice with the sacred
breath or the sacred word,

00:24:36.390 --> 00:24:38.710 align:middle line:90%
it's about intentionality.

00:24:38.710 --> 00:24:43.250 align:middle line:84%
In, say, mindfulness meditation
coming from Buddhism,

00:24:43.250 --> 00:24:45.980 align:middle line:84%
the practice is a
profound practice,

00:24:45.980 --> 00:24:49.860 align:middle line:84%
but perhaps it's more about
attention and awareness.

00:24:49.860 --> 00:24:52.850 align:middle line:84%
You're changing and transforming
your attention/awareness

00:24:52.850 --> 00:24:54.100 align:middle line:90%
as you go up that mountaintop.

00:24:54.100 --> 00:24:56.350 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That's a huge
piece, especially when we're

00:24:56.350 --> 00:24:59.310 align:middle line:84%
in this place of diffused
awareness and diffused

00:24:59.310 --> 00:25:00.930 align:middle line:90%
attention.

00:25:00.930 --> 00:25:04.080 align:middle line:84%
To have a practice that
allows you to get back

00:25:04.080 --> 00:25:06.870 align:middle line:84%
to that place of centering
and attention/awareness

00:25:06.870 --> 00:25:09.460 align:middle line:84%
is a great, great
idea-- helps lower

00:25:09.460 --> 00:25:11.540 align:middle line:90%
stress and all sorts of things.

00:25:11.540 --> 00:25:14.060 align:middle line:84%
Could you give us an
example or take us

