And the eyes closed--
let's take a breath.

00:26:05.030 --> 00:26:08.290 align:middle line:90%


00:26:08.290 --> 00:26:10.850 align:middle line:84%
And so just to prepare,
there are three segments

00:26:10.850 --> 00:26:15.500 align:middle line:84%
to centering prayer-- the
initial, preparatory moment,

00:26:15.500 --> 00:26:17.660 align:middle line:84%
and then the body of
the practice, and then

00:26:17.660 --> 00:26:19.510 align:middle line:90%
the conclusion.

00:26:19.510 --> 00:26:23.210 align:middle line:84%
So just prepare
by perhaps calling

00:26:23.210 --> 00:26:27.550 align:middle line:84%
to mind your own sense of the
divine, your own sense of who

00:26:27.550 --> 00:26:30.100 align:middle line:90%
or what God is for you now.

00:26:30.100 --> 00:26:34.210 align:middle line:84%
And that could be God,
or it could be life.

00:26:34.210 --> 00:26:37.590 align:middle line:84%
It could be a mystery
that you're not sure of.

00:26:37.590 --> 00:26:38.865 align:middle line:90%
But just call that to mind.

00:26:38.865 --> 00:26:45.300 align:middle line:90%


00:26:45.300 --> 00:26:50.540 align:middle line:84%
And have a sense of
opening your mind and heart

00:26:50.540 --> 00:26:55.520 align:middle line:84%
to the presence of the divine
as you know that to be.

00:26:55.520 --> 00:27:02.260 align:middle line:90%


00:27:02.260 --> 00:27:07.070 align:middle line:84%
And now, rather than
thinking about God,

00:27:07.070 --> 00:27:12.580 align:middle line:84%
let a word come to you
of one or two syllables

00:27:12.580 --> 00:27:17.920 align:middle line:84%
that expresses
your "yes" to God.

00:27:17.920 --> 00:27:19.810 align:middle line:90%
It could be yes.

00:27:19.810 --> 00:27:20.880 align:middle line:90%
It could be God.

00:27:20.880 --> 00:27:23.150 align:middle line:90%
It could be Shalom.

00:27:23.150 --> 00:27:25.900 align:middle line:84%
And let it come to you
as if it were floating up

00:27:25.900 --> 00:27:28.620 align:middle line:84%
from the depths of
a deep pool of water

00:27:28.620 --> 00:27:30.210 align:middle line:90%
to the surface of your mind.

00:27:30.210 --> 00:27:35.860 align:middle line:90%


00:27:35.860 --> 00:27:41.870 align:middle line:84%
And then, just
listen to that word

00:27:41.870 --> 00:27:45.260 align:middle line:90%
as it prays itself in your mind.

00:27:45.260 --> 00:27:50.186 align:middle line:84%
That is, rather than trying
to grind away on the word,

00:27:50.186 --> 00:27:51.850 align:middle line:90%
let the word be there.

00:27:51.850 --> 00:27:55.390 align:middle line:90%


00:27:55.390 --> 00:27:58.552 align:middle line:84%
Let it exist on the
stream of consciousness

00:27:58.552 --> 00:27:59.385 align:middle line:90%
with other thoughts.

00:27:59.385 --> 00:28:02.370 align:middle line:90%


00:28:02.370 --> 00:28:05.290 align:middle line:84%
Ever so gently,
return to it when

00:28:05.290 --> 00:28:07.035 align:middle line:84%
you're thinking about
another thought.

00:28:07.035 --> 00:28:10.120 align:middle line:90%


00:28:10.120 --> 00:28:14.120 align:middle line:84%
And in this moment,
just be willing to let

00:28:14.120 --> 00:28:18.010 align:middle line:84%
go of the word, the
form, and rest your mind

00:28:18.010 --> 00:28:19.760 align:middle line:90%
and heart in openness.

00:28:19.760 --> 00:28:25.720 align:middle line:90%


00:28:25.720 --> 00:28:27.970 align:middle line:84%
And then, of course, you'll
begin thinking again.

00:28:27.970 --> 00:28:30.860 align:middle line:90%
Return to the word.

00:28:30.860 --> 00:28:35.610 align:middle line:84%
And because this is a quick
dose, let go of the word.

00:28:35.610 --> 00:28:38.710 align:middle line:84%
And then, as you move into
conclusion, just take a moment

00:28:38.710 --> 00:28:42.010 align:middle line:84%
and perhaps offer
a prayer in words

00:28:42.010 --> 00:28:45.120 align:middle line:84%
quietly within for
the suffering world,

00:28:45.120 --> 00:28:50.070 align:middle line:84%
for someone or some
situation in life.

00:28:50.070 --> 00:28:56.750 align:middle line:90%


00:28:56.750 --> 00:28:57.590 align:middle line:90%
Amen.

00:28:57.590 --> 00:28:59.760 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Mmm.

00:28:59.760 --> 00:29:00.460 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:29:00.460 --> 00:29:01.890 align:middle line:90%
That was beautiful.

