I tend to have the busy
mind, but that's what I do.

00:30:16.680 --> 00:30:19.980 align:middle line:84%
And that state was--
it was-- floating

00:30:19.980 --> 00:30:22.520 align:middle line:84%
was a great word
for it because I

00:30:22.520 --> 00:30:24.840 align:middle line:84%
