00:30:24.840 --> 00:30:27.010 align:middle line:84%
Even though I love
to be grounded,

00:30:27.010 --> 00:30:30.900 align:middle line:84%
sometimes it's nice to just
release from that grounding

00:30:30.900 --> 00:30:33.660 align:middle line:84%
and reestablish
it in a new space.

00:30:33.660 --> 00:30:34.750 align:middle line:90%
>>FRENETTE: Exactly.

