you would really develop
that so that you could then

00:30:59.730 --> 00:31:03.300 align:middle line:84%
integrate that ground,
that silent ground,

00:31:03.300 --> 00:31:05.840 align:middle line:84%
into your thoughts
and emotions in life.

00:31:05.840 --> 00:31:09.510 align:middle line:84%
Because it's not like we want
to walk around being spacey.

00:31:09.510 --> 00:31:12.830 align:middle line:84%
But to have that freedom,
to have that experience--

00:31:12.830 --> 00:31:15.370 align:middle line:84%
a deepening experience
